Tuy nhien viec mua ban nay la hoat dong binh thuong phap luat khong cam nen UBND xa chi biet van dong nguoi dan khong ban.Ong Pham Minh Dao danh gia “O ta da co tinh trang nguoi ta khong mua ca con trau con bo ma chi mua mong nen dan tim mong trau mong bo de ban
Bay gio thuong lai dat ra chuyen mua la dieu kho lam phan nguoi dan can tien di hai la tuoi phoi kho ban thi khong kheo lai pha hoai san xuat nen can phai canh giac”.Theo Tuoi Tre
